Do not show raw JSON only.
Also render:
- profile summary card
- key strengths
- AI-interpreted contribution type
- best-fit project role
- recommended collaboration value

For writers:
show themes, tone, genre, creative goal, audience fit

For actors:
show artistic identity, emotional range, archetype fit, format fit

For reviewers:
show review focus, standards, specialization, evaluation lens

Also include a collapsible raw JSON panel for demo credibility.

