10. Role Placement UX Logic
The frontend must help users get into the right role.

Implement this logic:
- if the user’s questionnaire is strongly weighted toward creation of ideas, recommend Writer
- if strongly weighted toward performance and emotional embodiment, recommend Actor
- if strongly weighted toward evaluation and feedback, recommend Reviewer
- if strongly weighted toward professional validation, recommend Specialist

If confidence is low, show:
- "You may fit multiple roles"
and present top 2 roles with:
- primary recommendation
- secondary recommendation

Allow manual override, but always explain the recommended default.

11. Demo Mode Toggle
Add a demo mode switch in the UI:
- Demo Mode ON uses local sample datasets and a sample writer project
- Demo Mode OFF uses live user input only

This helps the hackathon demo move quickly.

