17. Hackathon Presentation Goal
The UI must make judges immediately understand:
- this platform is not just content generation
- this platform discovers role fit
- this platform matches people by contribution
- this platform assembles collaboration
- this platform turns collaboration into a YouTube-ready concept

Prioritize clarity, credibility, and demo smoothness over unnecessary complexity.

Build the frontend so the role placement experience feels intelligent, role-specific, and visually clear enough that a first-time viewer instantly understands where each type of user belongs in byDebut.